title: Rodney Ellis
added: Ellis chaired the Board of Directors for the [[Innocence Project]] from 2003 to 2017. He now serves as a member of the Founders' Circle for the Innocence Project. He co-chairs the [[National Conference of State Legislatures]] Task Force on International Relations. He also serves on the [[National Conference of State Legislatures]] Executive Committee, the [[Lyndon B. Johnson|LBJ]] Foundation Board of Trustees, and the [[Council on Foreign Relations]].<ref>[http://www.senate.state.tx.us/75r/senate/members/dist13/dist13.htm Texas Senate website] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110803103356/http://www.senate.state.tx.us/75r/Senate/members/dist13/dist13.htm |date=2011-08-03 }}</ref>
